		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">32.409-1</ph> Recommendation for approval.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">If recommending approval, the contracting officer shall transmit the following, under agency procedures, to the approving authority:</p>
			      <ol id="d2073e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2087e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Contract data, including-</p>
					          <ol id="d2073e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2087e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Identification and date of the award;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2087e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Citation of the appropriation;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2087e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Type and dollar amount of the contract;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2087e57" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Items to be supplied, schedule of deliveries or performance, and status of any deliveries or performance;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2087e66" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contract fee or profit contemplated; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2087e76" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(6)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                A copy of the contract, if available.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2087e87" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contractor’s request and supporting information.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2087e96" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            A report on the contractor’s past performance, responsibility, technical ability, and plant capacity.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2087e105" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Comments on-</p>
					          <ol id="d2073e111" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2087e115" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contractor’s need for advance payments; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2087e124" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Potential Government benefits from the contract performance.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2087e135" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Proposed advance payment contract terms, including proposed security requirements.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2087e145" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The findings, determination, and authorization (see <xref href="FAR-i1082814.dita#i1082814"
                        base="i1082814"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.410</xref>).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2087e157" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The recommendation for approval of the advance payment request.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2087e166" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(h)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Justification of any proposal for waiver of interest charges (see <xref href="FAR-i1082705.dita#i1082705"
                        base="i1082705"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.407</xref>).</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
